citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 11:00 a.m. to 11:30
a.m. on June 6, 2023.
Attempts to make contact with the licensee were done by knocking on the door, honking the GOV's horn, waiting for 30
minutes, and calling and leaving a voicemail.
End Section
